"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-06-24-New-sculpture-by-artist-Saar-unveiled-in-Paris-to-mark-Olympic-Day-1uGJanM0H1S-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CGTN  Copied  A sculpture is unveiled for the Olympic Day commemorations in Paris, France, June 23, 2024.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 281, \"end\": 286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999758515518, \"rank\": 2.41485189965223e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 288, \"end\": 294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.987243169474635, \"rank\": 0.006704385128548317, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/IOC MEDIA  A sculpture was unveiled on Sunday for this year's Olympic Day commemorations in Paris, where the 2024 Summer Olympic Games will get underway on July 26.\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 404, \"end\": 409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999758515518, \"rank\": 2.41485189965223e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The figurine was created by American visual artist Alison Saar and uncovered under sunny skies in the presence of International Olympic Committee (IOC) President Thomas Bach among other dignitaries.\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 506, \"end\": 514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999937304747702, \"rank\": 4.132591628368555e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 529, \"end\": 540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_Saar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alison Saar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_Saar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_Saar\"}, {\"begin\": 592, \"end\": 629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 640, \"end\": 651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As part of the Olympic Art Visions project, the IOC selects artists to create works inspired by sports and Olympic values to be installed in public spaces around host cities.\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 726, \"end\": 729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.479146705902905e-13, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The piece by Saar centers around a female figure conjuring a flame, which acts as a beacon to illuminate the world's path to a brighter and more harmonious future.\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 867, \"end\": 871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saarland\", \"score\": 0.7322296036658433, \"rank\": 0.3591540544174223, \"text\": \"Saar\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saarland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saarland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sport, much like art, is about capturing the hearts and minds of people with inspirational accomplishments,\\\" Bach said.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1129, \"end\": 1133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999999998624389, \"rank\": 1.3745241514479534e-10, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Thank you, dear Alison (Saar), for your contribution to blend sport and culture in such a magnificent way.\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1165, \"end\": 1169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saarland\", \"score\": 0.7322296036658433, \"rank\": 0.3591540544174223, \"text\": \"Saar\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saarland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saarland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is also what the Olympic Games are about \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 to bring all the different cultures of the world together in a peaceful competition \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 and for dialogue.\\\"\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Salon rises from our past histories, representing our present and the urgent need for peace and dignity for all,\\\" Saar said.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1521, \"end\": 1525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saarland\", \"score\": 0.7322296036658433, \"rank\": 0.3591540544174223, \"text\": \"Saar\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saarland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saarland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A female figure sits in the center of the work, and in the palm of her hand, she conjures a flame, a beacon that illuminates our path towards a brighter and more harmonious future.\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In her other hand, she holds olive branches, a metaphor for peace and reconciliation.\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1799, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Encircled by six chairs, she invites us to sit together to represent the diversity of cultures, to share our common experiences and humanity.\\\"\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1942, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 2204, \"entities\": []}]}"